ation of how the registry would be applied with respect to children with e-mail accounts.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Authorization to implement","label":"b Authorization to implement","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s7708/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s7708","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs7708%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Commission may establish and implement the plan, but not earlier than 9 months after .December 16, 2003","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}
